{"tid":1917480,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警稱去年新界 999 緊急求救回應率達 98% 數字無計 7.21 當日屬「個別」數字","createTime":"2020-03-09T13:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T14:25:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a629bab52a6319f8f4751ceac96def29a2c0b27e","tid":1917480,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T13:40:24.000Z","msg":"警稱去年新界 999 緊急求救回應率達 98% 數字無計 7.21 當日屬「個別」數字<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wsm_lXvNS_o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fwsm_lXvNS_o&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=7857dbff\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wsm_lXvNS_o</a><br />\n<br />\nStand News 立場新聞<br />\n45.6K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n全文：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2VY59NC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VY59NC&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=8072df76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2VY59NC</a><br />\n<br />\n上月發表的《財政預算案》附上警務處報告，指 2019 年的「緊急求救召喚」數目為 84,276，報告亦提到於 15 分鐘內回應新界區緊急求救電話的比率，2019 年是 97.9%。然而，政府在去年 7 月底也曾經提及，7.21 元朗襲擊當日，警方在 3 小時內收到 2.4 萬個緊急求救召喚。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員朱凱廸今日在立法會財委會會議上，質詢有關數字是否包含7.21 的緊急求救召喚，總警司（策劃及發展) 李雅麗確認，2019 年的「緊急求救召喚」數目，無計 7.21 的數字，「係唔包落去嘅」。<br />\n-------<br />\n<br />\n直播專頁：<a href=\"https://live.thestandnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.thestandnews.com&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=b6a58c3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.thestandnews.com&h=2429a784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://live.thestandnews.com</a><br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/thestandnews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fthestandnews&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM1cETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=5a08e505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/thestandnews</a><br />\nTelegram：<a href=\"https://t.me/thestandnews\" data-sr-url=\"htt